	,"x4freetext":[" The outgoing reaction residues were"
		,"distinguished based on their energy loss determined"
		,"in the S800 ionization chamber and the time of flight"
		,"measured between the object position of the analysis"
		,"beam line and the plastic scintillator at the back of"
		,"the S800 focal plane."]
